BWsem.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSmeg\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSmall / Mini Kettle - Pink\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf the full-size kettle is a little pricey, this mini kettle is a cheaper alternative.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eDe’Longhi has long been an\u003cem\u003e Ideal Home\u003c/em\u003e favourite, especially when it comes to their kettles. The Argento Kettle has a stylish, sleek look and a high-quality finish. It’s fast-boiling and with a large capacity, perfect for busy households.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt also sits on a 360-degree swivel base for ultimate convenience. Not only this, but the Argento Kettle features a triple safety protection, including auto-shut off, thermal cut off and automatic shut off when lifted.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat’s most striking about this kettle is its pretty pastel colourway and chrome details. \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/kitchen/pastel-kitchen-ideas\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/all-rooms/kitchen/pastel-kitchen-ideas\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ePastel kitchens\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e have been a big trend this year, so opting for small kitchen appliances in your preferred shade is an easy way to adopt the trend.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-fmPdXWShUqjpNBqQgrgDz\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eI’d also argue that pastel shades work well with \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/kitchen/kitchen-ideas/cream-kitchen-ideas-217956\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/kitchen/kitchen-ideas/cream-kitchen-ideas-217956\"\u003eneutral kitchen colour schemes\u003c/a\u003e, so if your kitchen is white or cream, pastel pink, green and blue appliances will complement it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB.png\" alt=\"Delonghi 1700ml Argento Kettle and toaster in pink.\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/uVPpaQiudfn5C7T2k8crsB.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: De\u0026#39;Longhi)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut it has to be said, retro appliances don’t get much better than Smeg. Our\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/kitchen/smeg-toaster-and-kettle-review\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/kitchen/smeg-toaster-and-kettle-review\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e Smeg kettle and toaster review\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e found the classic kettle to be quick to boil, has a soft open lid, a 360-degree connection base and a built-in lime scale filter - perfect is descaling the kettle is one of your least favourite chores.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf your heart is set on a Smeg kettle, there is also a mini version available. In fact, it is currently \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=22735\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-1160390775324006969\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.debenhams.com%2Fproduct%2Fsmeg-klf05-retro-50-s-style-mini-kettle-1400w-0-8l_p-c91349fc-aafe-4d89-a012-1ebba58bb9fc%3Fcolour%3DWhite%26size%3DOne%2BSize%26istCompanyId%3D76f7277d-6e78-4dc2-aaff-1eb77fae16b0%26istFeedId%3D258a4886-8f3c-47ef-9369-d1eda8d84501%26istItemId%3Dmrmxalipl%26istBid%3Dt%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds%26gad_source%3D1%26gbraid%3D0AAAAABevdS5vVBn5Y7ONFLDc-J8Se-UXq%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjwt8zABhDKARIsAHXuD7YhAkm_TgRuI--C7qpGA0hN4C41YB6TYiUNo8RoUmWthNhhJbqLh5QaAlCnEALw_wcB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.debenhams.com/product/smeg-klf05-retro-50-s-style-mini-kettle-1400w-0-8l_p-c91349fc-aafe-4d89-a012-1ebba58bb9fc?colour=White\u0026amp;size=One+Size\u0026amp;istCompanyId=76f7277d-6e78-4dc2-aaff-1eb77fae16b0\u0026amp;istFeedId=258a4886-8f3c-47ef-9369-d1eda8d84501\u0026amp;istItemId=mrmxalipl\u0026amp;istBid=t\u0026amp;gclsrc=aw.ds\u002